{"tha-ap558:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap558:0.2":"Yasavagga ","tha-ap558:0.3":"Uttarattheraapadana ","tha-ap558:1.1":"“Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap558:1.2":"battimsavaralakkhano; ","tha-ap558:1.3":"Vivekakamo bhagava, ","tha-ap558:1.4":"himavantamupagami. ","tha-ap558:2.1":"Ajjhogahetva himavantam, ","tha-ap558:2.2":"aggo karuniko muni; ","tha-ap558:2.3":"Pallankam abhujitvana, ","tha-ap558:2.4":"nisidi purisuttamo. ","tha-ap558:3.1":"Vijjadharo tada asim, ","tha-ap558:3.2":"antalikkhacaro aham; ","tha-ap558:3.3":"Tisulam sukatam gayha, ","tha-ap558:3.4":"gacchami ambare tada. ","tha-ap558:4.1":"Pabbatagge yatha aggi, ","tha-ap558:4.2":"punnamayeva candima; ","tha-ap558:4.3":"Vanam obhasate buddho, ","tha-ap558:4.4":"salarajava phullito. ","tha-ap558:5.1":"Vanagga nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap558:5.2":"buddharamsibhidhavare; ","tha-ap558:5.3":"Nalaggivannasankasa, ","tha-ap558:5.4":"disva cittam pasadayim. ","tha-ap558:6.1":"Vicinam addasam puppham, ","tha-ap558:6.2":"kanikaram devagandhikam; ","tha-ap558:6.3":"Tini pupphani adaya, ","tha-ap558:6.4":"buddhasetthamapujayim. ","tha-ap558:7.1":"Buddhassa anubhavena, ","tha-ap558:7.2":"tini pupphani me tada; ","tha-ap558:7.3":"Uddham vanta adhopatta, ","tha-ap558:7.4":"chayam kubbanti satthuno. ","tha-ap558:8.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap558:8.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap558:8.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap558:8.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap558:9.1":"Tattha me sukatam byamham, ","tha-ap558:9.2":"kanikariti nayati; ","tha-ap558:9.3":"Satthiyojanamubbedham, ","tha-ap558:9.4":"timsayojanavitthatam. ","tha-ap558:10.1":"Sahassakandam satabhendu, ","tha-ap558:10.2":"dhajalu haritamayam; ","tha-ap558:10.3":"Satasahassaniyyuha, ","tha-ap558:10.4":"byamhe patubhavimsu me. ","tha-ap558:11.1":"Sonnamaya manimaya, ","tha-ap558:11.2":"lohitankamayapi ca; ","tha-ap558:11.3":"Phalikapi ca pallanka, ","tha-ap558:11.4":"yenicchaka yadicchaka. ","tha-ap558:12.1":"Maharahanca sayanam, ","tha-ap558:12.2":"tulika vikatiyutam; ","tha-ap558:12.3":"Uddhalominca ekantam, ","tha-ap558:12.4":"bimbohanasamayutam. ","tha-ap558:13.1":"Bhavana nikkhamitvana, ","tha-ap558:13.2":"caranto devacarikam; ","tha-ap558:13.3":"Yatha icchami gamanam, ","tha-ap558:13.4":"devasanghapurakkhato. ","tha-ap558:14.1":"Pupphassa hettha titthami, ","tha-ap558:14.2":"uparicchadanam mama; ","tha-ap558:14.3":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","tha-ap558:14.4":"kanikarehi chaditam. ","tha-ap558:15.1":"Satthituriyasahassani, ","tha-ap558:15.2":"sayapatam upatthahum; ","tha-ap558:15.3":"Parivarenti mam niccam, ","tha-ap558:15.4":"rattindivamatandita. ","tha-ap558:16.1":"Tattha naccehi gitehi, ","tha-ap558:16.2":"talehi vaditehi ca; ","tha-ap558:16.3":"Ramami khidda ratiya, ","tha-ap558:16.4":"modami kamakamaham. ","tha-ap558:17.1":"Tattha bhutva pivitva ca, ","tha-ap558:17.2":"modami tidase tada; ","tha-ap558:17.3":"Nariganehi sahito, ","tha-ap558:17.4":"modami byamhamuttame. ","tha-ap558:18.1":"Satanam pancakkhattunca, ","tha-ap558:18.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap558:18.3":"Satanam tinikkhattunca, ","tha-ap558:18.4":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap558:18.5":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap558:18.6":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap558:19.1":"Bhave bhave samsaranto, ","tha-ap558:19.2":"mahabhogam labhamaham; ","tha-ap558:19.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","tha-ap558:19.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:20.1":"Duve bhave samsarami, ","tha-ap558:20.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","tha-ap558:20.3":"Annam gatim na janami, ","tha-ap558:20.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:21.1":"Duve kule pajayami, ","tha-ap558:21.2":"khattiye capi brahmane; ","tha-ap558:21.3":"Nice kule na janami, ","tha-ap558:21.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:22.1":"Hatthiyanam assayanam, ","tha-ap558:22.2":"sivikam sandamanikam; ","tha-ap558:22.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap558:22.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:23.1":"Dasiganam dasaganam, ","tha-ap558:23.2":"nariyo samalankata; ","tha-ap558:23.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap558:23.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:24.1":"Koseyyakambaliyani, ","tha-ap558:24.2":"khomakappasikani ca; ","tha-ap558:24.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap558:24.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:25.1":"Navavattham navaphalam, ","tha-ap558:25.2":"navaggarasabhojanam; ","tha-ap558:25.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap558:25.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:26.1":"Imam khada imam bhunja, ","tha-ap558:26.2":"imamhi sayane saya; ","tha-ap558:26.3":"Labhami sabbamevetam, ","tha-ap558:26.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:27.1":"Sabbattha pujito homi, ","tha-ap558:27.2":"yaso accuggato mama; ","tha-ap558:27.3":"Mahapakkho sada homi, ","tha-ap558:27.4":"abhejjapariso sada; ","tha-ap558:27.5":"Natinam uttamo homi, ","tha-ap558:27.6":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:28.1":"Sitam unham na janami, ","tha-ap558:28.2":"parilaho na vijjati; ","tha-ap558:28.3":"Atho cetasikam dukkham, ","tha-ap558:28.4":"hadaye me na vijjati. ","tha-ap558:29.1":"Suvannavanno hutvana, ","tha-ap558:29.2":"samsarami bhavabhave; ","tha-ap558:29.3":"Vevanniyam na janami, ","tha-ap558:29.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:30.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap558:30.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap558:30.3":"Savatthiyam pure jato, ","tha-ap558:30.4":"mahasalesu addhake. ","tha-ap558:31.1":"Panca kamagune hitva, ","tha-ap558:31.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap558:31.3":"Jatiya sattavassoham, ","tha-ap558:31.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap558:32.1":"Upasampadayi buddho, ","tha-ap558:32.2":"gunamannaya cakkhuma; ","tha-ap558:32.3":"Taruno pujaniyoham, ","tha-ap558:32.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:33.1":"Dibbacakkhuvisuddham me, ","tha-ap558:33.2":"samadhikusalo aham; ","tha-ap558:33.3":"Abhinnaparamippatto, ","tha-ap558:33.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:34.1":"Patisambhida anuppatto, ","tha-ap558:34.2":"iddhipadesu kovido; ","tha-ap558:34.3":"Dhammesu paramippatto, ","tha-ap558:34.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:35.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap558:35.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap558:35.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap558:35.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap558:36.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap558:36.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap558:36.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap558:37.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap558:37.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap558:37.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap558:38.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap558:38.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap558:38.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap558:39.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma uttaro thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap558:40.1":"Uttarattherassapadanam chattham. "}